# Manual Assist rules
- Manual Assist is NOT automation of posting; it is a helper flow:
  - Open the upload page in the user’s browser
  - Reveal/select the local file (in-app UI) so the user can drag/drop or pick it easily
  - Copy caption + hashtags to clipboard
- Always show the user a confirmation/toast when clipboard content changes.
- Never auto-fill credentials or attempt automated posting.
